{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of the worst thing happened that people, due to the fact that we were not having washing facilities and bathrooms and so on, lice was very predominant.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And lice, in turn, created illnesses, like typhus and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were slightly a little bit puzzled that why just suddenly like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We knew about all this disinfection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By-- by that time we were seasoned into what was going on, and we were-- thought maybe they're doing something funny.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe it's another little extermination affair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But so it-- it's a small camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why should they do it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As it happens, it was a perfectly legitimate disinfection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got our clothing cleaned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got it back clean and dry and warm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a very nice-- maybe as a Christmas present, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or a New Year's present they give.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So for a few days we felt refreshed again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, having come back to Buchenwald, and having described you what the circumstances were, we were put in the middle lager, Block 59, which mainly sort of ill people and people halfway out and halfway in this world existed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some stronger, some weaker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the summer of '44 when we were in Buchenwald, we knew that there were two hospitals-- the Kleinrivier and the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What we didn't know was that in the same middle lager, they turn block number 61 into a killing block where they give the lethal injections.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And literally, as they went around the camp, because they couldn't send back to Auschwitz people anymore, they selected the ill or not so ill people on a regular basis, and they were allowed to go into so-called hospital.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the purpose of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
